::Primal Prime/Cheetor::

    Primal and Cheetor came across Striker and the new bot Hot Rod.
    "Hey! Fellow Maximals! How's it shaken?" Cheetor asked.
    "Allow me to introduce myself, I am known as Primal. You look 
familiar...do I know you? (Talking to Hot Rod)" Primal said.
    "Yea, and I'm Cheetor." Cheetor said relizing he forgot to introduce 
himself.

(Just a thanks to Hot Rod for landing on the planet, it's gonna help my 
story. Primal Prime has Optimus Prime's spark from the Matrix mixed with a 
protoforms spark, so he's all new.)
